snippet: Colorado State senior Emmanuel Omogbo's right basketball shoe is a dedication to his parents, their names written in black marker with "RIP" alongside. The left one, a tribute to his niece and nephew....
lead_paragraph: Colorado State senior Emmanuel Omogbo's right basketball shoe is a dedication to his parents, their names written in black marker with "RIP" alongside. The left one, a tribute to his niece and nephew.

headline.main: Omogbo Leads Rams Year After Death of Parents in House Fire
headline.print_headline: Omogbo Leads Rams Year After Death of Parents in House Fire
